  "text": "Tissues were fixed for 24-48 h in buffered formalin (4%) and embedded in paraffin. Sections were cut at 5 µm and stained with haematoxylin and eosin. FACS analysis was performed on fresh liver and kidney tissue as described [CITATION_1] .",
